 ploads/event/volsocial1_20260317202827648089.png
DESCRIPTION:Join us in Indianapolis for a special ACLU of Indiana Voluntee
 r Social! Whether you're fired up about protecting civil liberties\, ready
  to stand up for LGBTQ+ rights\, or just curious about how to get involved
  — we want to meet you. Learn how you can get involved and stay engaged.
  Dinner and N/A drinks provided! Please register to see the event details.
LOCATION:Indianapolis\, IN
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/acluin/event/896878/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Central Indiana (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
