 Volunteer opportunities. Register for this webinar to get trained on what 
 it means to be a volunteer with the ACLU of Indiana. Sign up for a time th
 at works for you! Once you have attended one New Volunteer Orientation you
  do not need to sign up again. These happen on a quarterly basis to get pe
 ople trained and signed up!
